Ms. Eom must be so upset.

17
00:01:29,970 --> 00:01:31,110
(Pregnancy Journal, Maeng Gong Hee)

18
00:01:31,110 --> 00:01:32,880
"Pregnancy Journal, Maeng Gong Hee."

19
00:01:34,410 --> 00:01:35,979
Pregnancy.

20
00:01:38,050 --> 00:01:39,819
