Don't go!

27
00:02:35,539 --> 00:02:36,539
Tonight,

28
00:02:37,410 --> 00:02:38,840
I don't see a single star.

29
00:02:41,579 --> 00:02:43,410
Without you here,

30
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:47,289
I don't have anyone
to eat late-night snacks with!

31
00:02:48,789 --> 00:02:49,789
This voice...

32
00:02:49,850 --> 00:02:51,460
Hey, Gu Dan Soo!

33
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:53,759
Maeng Gong Hee?

34
00:02:59,130 --> 00:03:00,729
Why do I have to order so much...

35
00:03:00,729 --> 00:03:03,169
just to have some tteokbokki
delivered?

36
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,100
I don't have anyone to go
to the convenience store with...

37
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:07,870
